                <h2>Crafting Exceptional Coffee Experiences</h2>
                <p>Hello! I'm Harerimana Nadjib, a passionate and skilled barista with a deep love for coffee culture and craftsmanship. With years of hands-on experience behind the espresso machine, I specialize in latte art, precise brewing techniques, and delivering exceptional coffee experiences to every customer.</p>
                <p>Becoming a barista wasn't just a job—it was a calling. I fell in love with the smell of fresh ground beans, the sound of steaming milk, and the smiles from happy customers. To me, coffee means connection, creativity, and calm in a cup.</p>
